
The structure of the project will be as follows:
- multiple clients can connect to the server
- clients and the server can send information to each other
- the groups of information that will be shared between the nodes:
    - information sent to all clients
    - information sent to specific clients
    - information recieved from specific clients
- the information sent to all clients can be changed continuosly, or when there is something to send
- get this thing working for a simple chat server
